{"tid":2514381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台物資抵印度 陸疑阻氧氣機出境","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:45:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d98fae1a57cc3677c34084f060faeb604e4633cb","tid":2514381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/D42OEVCE5JCOXCU3L3IDZY53LM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FD42OEVCE5JCOXCU3L3IDZY53LM%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=688e2552\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FD42OEVCE5JCOXCU3L3IDZY53LM%2F&h=0b9a72d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/D42OEVCE5JCOXCU3L3IDZY53LM/</a><br />\n<br />\n台物資抵印度 陸疑阻氧氣機出境<br />\n<br />\n印度疫情慘況成為全球焦點。在北京多次聲稱要向印度提供醫療物資的同時，台灣昨日亦搶閘將首批援助送到印度。該批包括150部氧氣機及500個氧氣鋼瓶的物資，由中華航空貨機運往印度首都新德里，貨物包裝上貼有「來自台灣的愛」（Love From Taiwan）字樣標記。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：送米送油 全國僅18.9%人打疫苗  上海邀女團派福利谷針<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0XLHc53LouWY5PjAvqrxyY31Ixo=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PZ23TX7WNBDZZMI3G72UUWBXC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0XLHc53LouWY5PjAvqrxyY31Ixo%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPZ23TX7WNBDZZMI3G72UUWBXC4.jpg&h=9d5ec06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台首批援助物資印有「來自台灣的愛」字樣。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡霞譴責政法委無人性<br />\n<br />\n印度醫療物資緊缺，有印度影星投訴嘗試將氧氣機等物資運返印度時，在大陸受阻。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在中國，早前政法委官方微博發文嘲諷印度疫情死亡人數風波仍未平息，雖然該帖文已被刪，網民質疑：「有膽發沒膽接受人民的評論？ 」。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n旅居美國的中共中央黨校前教授蔡霞則發聲譴責政法委毫無人性。她指，印度曾在中國疫情肆虐時援助中國，今次中共的嘲諷「毫不掩飾他們反人性反人類的邪惡本質」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/微博/Twitter"},{"pid":"c1dead9cba9628f05c0421d2dfaa71598af370b7","tid":2514381,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c371993f23b774c88d6a94c3489bb3e152ce1c0","tid":2514381,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"Fucking Chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041db0a57501bcd02b2abe3ba198ba351b59f232","tid":2514381,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"繁體支那有物資，殘體支那有乜呢"},{"pid":"344dff2c5ce7f52dff093c76fa721c1bd7eec9a4","tid":2514381,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"041db0a57501bcd02b2abe3ba198ba351b59f232","tid":2514381,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"繁體支那有物資，殘體支那有乜呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}